column2: SELECT    e.plate,e.mjd,e.fiberID,   e.sigmaStars,e.sigmaStarsErr,    s.velDisp , st.vdisp_median into mydb.MyTable_# from specObjAll AS s   JOIN emissionLinesPort e on s.specObjid = e.specObjid    JOIN stellarMassPCAWisc st on st.specObjid = s.specObjid   JOIN MyDB.MyTable m on s.bestObjid = m.objid
